217b2db14c69a3ac.voiceContent: I want to go adventuring with you into the unknown, collect strange new ingredients from all over Teyvat, and invent new recipes for you to sample!

65d238d77d26e7cd.voiceContent: Well, sometimes, customers get to talking to each other, and they chat for so long that their food starts to get cold...

5434e7c9ecf19e71.voiceContent: You seem very quiet... Y—You don't like the idea?

ecde1c836d4c914b.voiceContent: The best part is seeing smiles on my customers' faces. Those are the real fruits of my labor!

e65f8eb831353d58.voiceContent: Combining existing ingredients in new ways already allows for countless variations in flavor.

9da39ca45105619f.voiceContent: Still... it can be difficult at times.

5093e32adf707408.voiceContent: Get some rest! Tomorrow, I'll make something tasty for you!

bf83bc672ad207db.voiceContent: I know I shouldn't really interrupt them, but reheating the food just ruins the flavor...

d669e9c21c7c15e0.voiceContent: Anything to put a smile on your face!

11a123afb3e3bd4a.voiceContent: I was just coming up with a new dish... don't worry, nothing too strange!

93d5aa2e1695e7af.voiceContent: But even so, it's still the thing I wanna do most!

645798729dc3fed0.voiceContent: Phew! ...You scared the heck out of me.

c412a878d8357bf5.voiceContent: Hehe, I feel a lot better after talking to you about it, though.

437d6b55999dda3b.voiceContent: Um — what I mean is... I'll definitely get your opinion before acting on any eureka moments!

530afbb8426fa057.voiceContent: Ahh... the more I consider it, the more I think nothing could ever make me happier!

3d4fbfdef8f6a6a2.voiceContent: *sigh* Yeah, I know... I guess I just have to learn to not let it get to me.

b4d5e8b6993f2599.voiceContent: ...It's really nothing to do with rare ingredients, secret recipes, or anything like that.

f6ee1ee05b8a733c.voiceContent: Um... That does happen... but I wasn't talking so much about the food as...

474ef9811f4b7027.voiceContent: Taste-testing is all part of the adventure!

681ce8afedd55ad9.voiceContent: But really... Don't worry about it!

e7e5f78923af4ab3.voiceContent: A—Anyway, I'll make sure to keep working on my cooking... a—and any other skills that might come in handy!

50e99c9da599e3df.voiceContent: The trick is to keep playing with different pairings — I've got plenty of new concepts to try out!

365a29a03fa0537a.voiceContent: I want to go adventuring with you!

be23f95dd9ecdbf2.voiceContent: A—Also, I won't slow you down when we're out in the wilderness!

a38a1c7cc4c43b8b.voiceContent: Just a shame more of them aren't potential ingredients...

97c0dde727b78ac5.voiceContent: It is! I knew you'd get it!

ee07489517cd48a5.voiceContent: Absolutely! Service isn't for a while yet, so there's nothing on the stove.

4491baadccf2e036.voiceContent: I just use my own methods and try to bring out the best in every ingredient! Certainly seems to satisfy my customers.

aac9a3c174894752.voiceContent: Adventuring on an empty stomach is a recipe for disaster!

d2778dd2305180f0.voiceContent: I won't add any strange seasonings... promise!

f6ae8e957706aa14.voiceContent: I love it! Very cozy. And there are so many new and interesting things I've never seen before!

191838d0d1bb690d.voiceContent: Waah! Really? Great, I'll get cooking!

256e49a138957e9c.voiceContent: And if I encounter any serious enemies, I promise I won't cause any trouble. First sign of danger, I'll run as fast as I can...

93962a8ce90c6482.voiceContent: Yep! Gastronomy just makes me happy!

fb3ebaa7246c3e76.voiceContent: But, um... What would really make a difference is if you could taste-test them a—and give me some feedback.

3269e68e4cb924d7.voiceContent: Hmm... There isn't too much stocked here. I'll whip up some food for us, so could you go and help me buy some ingredients?

ab66f257603fcc7c.voiceContent: After that, I'll open another Wanmin Restaurant right here!

b0ac84969018f9ce.voiceContent: Of course, you can't skimp on ingredients — only the freshest will do!

90ceee451523590a.voiceContent: Awesome! This little street of eateries is pretty similar to Chihu Rock, but if you look closer, there are a lot of differences, too!

3393d29ff73b22f1.voiceContent: Chefs can't be picky about location! No matter what kitchen appliances there are, I'll be back to cooking like I normally do after a few practice rounds!

16e50c4e7ef9170d.voiceContent: Let's go look at different restaurants together and see what makes each place unique, okay?

289649f9f2158724.voiceContent: There are so many people... I hope everything goes smoothly on Hu Tao's end, so she can get back here and celebrate with us soon.

3e654ade3b64a087.voiceContent: Hehe, I was just kidding around. Happy Lantern Rite! Hope I didn't scare ya?

b0184c2b24500234.voiceContent: Good idea! Especially since it's festival season. I heard the Ministry of Civil Affairs is putting on a street fair with loads of cool stuff to do.

4fa756cd2b89006d.voiceContent: Well, I gave her a new outfit as a gift, but she's so used to her uniform that she's hesitant to try it on.

5c83f83a5ad16416.voiceContent: Hmm... Okay, fair enough. But don't take too long! And after the fair, how about we all have a meal at Wanmin Restaurant? My treat, of course.

e4293cd60ccfb4dc.voiceContent: A bright red one, of course! The color of prosperity, and the color of Lantern Rite.

a33beabdf5080af3.voiceContent: But just so you're aware... Hu Tao's not really been herself lately. Whenever I invite her to hang out, she either finds an excuse not to come, or spends the whole time staring into space.

21b4b8c63895c0ea.voiceContent: I've tried asking her what's wrong, but she won't even admit there's a problem. *sigh*... Anyway, so that outfit was my way of saying that I'm here as her friend, and I hope she'll feel better soon.

a21206ac4a861a39.voiceContent: Nope! The tailor happened to be in Liyue looking for a change of scenery and fresh inspiration. We got talking and really hit it off. So it was no trouble at all!

598dda126f2a6aab.voiceContent: Work-related? You mean the funeral parlor?

e55328e7b751b2fe.voiceContent: I noticed — which is why I stopped you! We can't disturb her now, or we won't get to see the brand-spanking-new Director Hu.

aeee681979ce1262.voiceContent: Your voice is as sweet as ever Hu Tao, but we're your friends. You can't hide how you're feeling from us, no matter how hard you may try.

09608621a890a885.voiceContent: Forget about work for now, Hu Tao. Come have fun with us!

1ceeacb48b02d3b8.voiceContent: Oh, stop. I'm just glad you like it.

aab901e7985ad0f4.voiceContent: What I'm looking for is a living being, but one you wouldn't normally cook with. It can fly, crawl or bounce, and even insects will do.

31ac41137900a563.voiceContent: Hee-hee, this is perfect! Come to me, my little treasure!

8235c5a36bf76a8e.voiceContent: Hope everything goes smoothly. And don't leave me hanging this time!

c406fd92139f8b28.voiceContent: I'm thinking, my latest creation! You know the one Drunken Plums in Snow!

669054eb71ae631b.voiceContent: Huh? Is no one gonna pick the Yunlai Angler? Even the Yuheng said that her sword-fighting style comes from the Yunlai Angler's rod-wielding techniques.

e5c607055f6137a4.voiceContent: Haha, has Xingqiu been getting you into light novels?

9232731495e3e046.voiceContent: Paimon, you're up! It's time to share your grand philosophy of life with everyone.

67ba40fd1c306135.voiceContent: Come on, enough with the debate already! Everyone's here now, so let's eat.

1755d50c5567342f.voiceContent: Paimon, did you forget about our special guest?

d177fb1c716bae8a.voiceContent: I think you mean two people, right? I'm just a chef — a good one, but it's not THAT much to get excited about. You don't need to include me just to be polite.

3608d5e826078f6b.voiceContent: Nope! They're toys that shoot fireworks! New to this year's festival. You should try them, Paimon.

7c4b1433fa2e9a3b.voiceContent: Promise you won't stand us up this time?

434a6171e3307ecd.voiceContent: Hee-hee, great minds think alike, dad!

bd33436879590dca.voiceContent: Dad, I brought some friends over! I'm cooking today! ...Hmm? Dad? Daaad...

d466477ac1940a3c.voiceContent: Go on, get Timaeus to Bubu Pharmacy. And don't forget to come eat when you're done!

652c7eb99af05357.voiceContent: Seriously? ...Haha, did Xingqiu tell you that? 'Cause it sounds like something right out of a martial arts novel!

43b5a08fea8e1908.voiceContent: Perfect! Hmm, Hu Tao should have joined us here by now... I guess her meeting overran. Why don't we head to the funeral parlor?

9df0de981921a443.voiceContent: Oh, are you looking for Hu Tao? She's supposed to meet us here so we can grab lunch. Why don't you come with? If you don't mind the extra company, of course.

66566acb45725171.voiceContent: Oh! I think I heard that one from a storyteller once — The Sanctification of Tao Du. So Tao Du is the giant tree...?

487baca19821067a.voiceContent: Haha, the Traveler's being especially nice today, checking in on everyone's wellbeing.

339cb0b2a4ea56ac.voiceContent: I heard from Hu Tao that she has a flaming staff handed down by her forebearers. Apparently, it has special powers, used for cleansing rituals...

a280caa9c686cb7d.voiceContent: But it could just be another one of her tall tales. ...Oh, you probably haven't met Hu Tao yet, have you? She's the director at the funeral parlor.

e36f1cc1de50284e.voiceContent: If I remember right, they were from several groups that joined forces... a Guizang one, a Lianshan one, and...

a26010c3f6ddb6df.voiceContent: It's honestly a little rich that you're out here telling everyone else to take care of themselves and keep a good work-life balance when you are apparently too busy to eat!

f50090a316080e8b.voiceContent: Haha, I was only kidding. I know Paimon loves to eat, but I think it'd take more than food to pry her away from your side.

4cb52ecd75b01176.voiceContent: Tracking you guys down, obviously! You really made me work for it, too.

482502bbc84a7d14.voiceContent: Keep this up, and I'll have to drag you to the dinner table and force feed you my delicious cooking against your will!

f62abcb4c08a79e5.voiceContent: Here we are, I present to you Chef Xiangling's newest creation Drunken Plums in Snow. You must be starving, surely? Go on, dig in!

aca63320e5495ec0.voiceContent: Anyway, enough about that — time for you guys to eat. Whatever your plans are after this, they'll go much better on a full stomach!

b9935cd63f192dd9.voiceContent: Hey guys! Are you finally done? I've been waiting forever!

8372d934d1cde271.voiceContent: Hehe, Xingqiu and I! He said he's been wanting to invite everyone out for a long time, but given the situation with his great-grandfather, he never had the time.

01b57f3d152dc4f0.voiceContent: But amazingly, on the night of the Lantern Rite, his great-grandfather suddenly woke up! Xingqiu was thrilled — and he was finally able to leave the house. So we met up right away and made a plan.

9236b6fc49361baa.voiceContent: At Yilong Wharf, later tonight! Xingqiu and the others are still out there. Oh, and Hu Tao said that we'll be joined by a special guest!

008b8b2b6aabb94e.voiceContent: But don't worry — we've agreed that this time, we're not gonna accept any more excuses from her.

8248ed23274be457.voiceContent: Yeah, tell me about it... She thinks being a director gives her a license to be a flake. It's like, unless there's a sizeable crowd coming, it's not worth my time.

1723e8f4088b8eb3.voiceContent: You'll see when you get there!

54ac3b0c1d71c29c.voiceContent: Don't worry, it definitely does! Your appetite represents an optimistic outlook on life Always eat to your heart's content, lest your chopsticks wither with regret!

ed61eac8bec91ff2.voiceContent: According to Xingqiu, his great-grandfather has been eating like Paimon since he woke up... so now, the family's biggest worry is that he'll get indigestion.

72bb5cc07e7a1e3b.voiceContent: Yep! They had a doctor take a look and everything. He'll be just fine.

bf9d391352e25c7d.voiceContent: You know what's up! Our get-together, of course!

50b91f1c3145e7ac.voiceContent: Yeah! You are free, right? You are not getting out of this without a very good reason!

c39055033f0e372d.voiceContent: Haha, don't worry. Save it for the dinner table, Paimon!

c535ee240574ffc8.voiceContent: Her work is incredible! Especially this Guoba hat. It's just as cute as the real Guoba!

847dbc0bedd9680f.voiceContent: Yeah, yeah, Director Hu has the most exquisite taste in the world, et cetera.

fe316e0283d5c904.voiceContent: Whoa, sounds amazing! So is this what's been keeping you busy these past few days? No wonder we still haven't had that meal together... I bet you've barely had a moment to breathe.

838aa7fa43866895.voiceContent: Once the ceremony's over, come for food with us, okay?

61886a55f652320e.voiceContent: Promise you won't stand us up this time?

d3b83beb0a2097fb.voiceContent: Fair enough... Wait, does that mean you're involved in tonight's ceremony thing? I heard the announcement from the Ministry of Civil Affairs.

51c4c9f34d52c1b2.voiceContent: Uh... Why get me involved? Can't you just give these to them yourself?

7304881cfd858289.voiceContent: I dunno, Hu Tao, you're kind of asking a lot of me there...

02976051a2c4c98e.voiceContent: I guess she's got more on her plate than we realized... Well, there's not much point in hanging around here. Why don't we go eat and come back later?

88e4ae5b0cca1bb1.voiceContent: Hey, Ferry. We're looking for Hu Tao, is she here?

8454c2495f64f497.voiceContent: It sounded like she's gonna be a while. Besides, I can always fire up the stove again once she's back.

c1aa0e398afd1fbd.voiceContent: Alright Ferry, we'll head off then. Can you let Hu Tao know where we are when she gets back?

e17ead22b266761d.voiceContent: #{NICKNAME}, help me put him in his place!

84138f1a811d881a.voiceContent: Whoa! My ingredients are attacking me!

c62d5cf178926443.voiceContent: Out of the frying pan, into the fire!

493a53cb2ab9e04a.voiceContent: Open sesame! Oh, now I'm hungry...

606d57dd72f4dcbc.voiceContent: None of this will go to waste!

48913ece9e527b42.voiceContent: Hello, nice to meet you! My name is Xiangling, I'm a chef from Liyue! My favorite place is the chicken... I mean, the kitchen! Ugh, I practiced so hard, but I still get nervous when introducing myself... Heh.

3836d37525004cc4.voiceContent: Is there time for a quick snack? I'll whip one up in no time!

0dbea15dab4ccdbb.voiceContent: I can't decide whether Pyro slimes taste better with salt and pepper or garlic and herbs...

88652f65eb9bcf72.voiceContent: If there's nothing better to do, we could go foraging for ingredients...

f04ea610d04b7aa2.voiceContent: Oh... I don't like the rain.

4abfc418ff0c5ec5.voiceContent: Wait... did I leave my apron outside to dry?

13f301b018a68983.voiceContent: The rain has stopped! Come with me, let's pick some matsutake.

42a03d12fa3d08d0.voiceContent: Anemo Slimes always come out in this weather. If you catch some, I'll make you a Slime Slushie!

b7cfce142fbda890.voiceContent: Perfect timing! Wanna get a few cooking supplies?

f1fb27e88b8e48cc.voiceContent: Lunch is ready! Come and get it while it lasts! *munching*

90692e122b59201a.voiceContent: You're just in time for a midnight snack! I made some barbecued lizard skewers. Well, don't just stand there — dig in!

0e89777dc80349aa.voiceContent: Hey! You're not sneaking off to get a midnight snack without me, are you? ...Bedtime? Oh. Well, good night then!

76bf35ce6abd21cd.voiceContent: You've seen the dragon in Mondstadt? How big was it? What!? No way! Imagine how big a steak a dragon that huge would make!

f2f370c4db9e297a.voiceContent: I'm much better at cooking than navigating... but if you do go out, definitely take me with you!

4cf88ecd0a03ee7d.voiceContent: Meeting you has really opened my eyes to things other than cooking. Like what? Well, such as... um... for example... I can't think when you put me on the spot! Forget it, I'll stick to cooking from now on. I have a new recipe for you to try, actually...

e3205b50aab72c71.voiceContent: Any time, night or day, I am always willing to make dishes everyone loves. I think the Archons agree with my passion, or else they wouldn't have given me this Vision, something even my master doesn't have... I know they want me to keep going!

0095b5a245b00546.voiceContent: If you get a stomach ache, a cup of herbal tea with Silk Flowers will clear it up in no time! Huh? Of course you can trust my herbal remedies! We chefs are expected to know a thing or two about medicine as well, you know!

e7062aeb8b70df64.voiceContent: I love onions! I've tried cutting them dozens of ways, and they still make me cry... No matter, I still love them!

c9cb01b0882239a4.voiceContent: I can smell Mist Grass! It must be Dr. Baizhu! What is he doing here? *Shocked* Are you OK? Do you feel faint? Is your stomach sore? Or is it a sore throat? I've got it, you're fatigued from all that adventuring! No?... You're fine? Phew! Otherwise, he would've made you drink some traditional herbal medicine — it's so bitter!

f84d23e149236e7f.voiceContent: That was the Tianquan! Did you see? She just walked past. Come here... closer... Let me tell you, she knows everything that happens in Liyue, so... keep a low profile, don't attract her attention!

a76d39cc5c9eaf40.voiceContent: Is Hu Tao picking on you too? Ugh, that prankster always waits till I least expect it, creeps up on me from behind and then... Boo! ...then laughs herself silly. Hmph. But I can handle it, and she does bring me fermented plum blossoms once in a while so I can make flower cakes... so I don't hold a grudge.

8036d94ae78d53a8.voiceContent: Chongyun? I always see him on his way to eat at Wanmin Restaurant with Xingqiu... Ah... or perhaps I should say I see him being dragged there by Xingqiu? Chongyun doesn't eat hot food. Every time the hot food arrives, Xingqiu politely apologizes and proceeds to try every dish. I just wanna dig in with him! The look on Chongyun's face is priceless. They're quite interesting, those two.

c8a05a20ac6a0b35.voiceContent: Ganyu? Oh... Oh yeah! I remember her — vegetarian, right? She doesn't come to the Wanmin Restaurant very often — but when she does, she sits alone in the corner and eats her meal in total silence. Poor girl, she seems kinda lonely... I always give her an extra-large portion because I feel sorry for her. Funniest thing is, she eats every last bite, every time! I wouldn't have guessed she had such an appetite just by looking at her.

6f838ee61ead886f.voiceContent: Hee-hee, I'm proud to call her my junior! She hasn't swung by the Wanmin Restaurant in ages, though. Maybe master is trying to protect her from me or something... Last time we hung out, I was about to dig into some fresh raw octopus from the Sea of Clouds, but not only did she stop me from eating it, she sent master to tell me off too! Ugh... Honestly, sometimes it feels like I'm the one who gets treated like the junior...

be32921c9c3a1194.voiceContent: Diona, from Springvale! Ah, I heard she mixes a great drink, so I came specifically to see her! I thought perhaps I could use her secrets in my cooking, and bring out more flavors. But the tips that she gave me — like soaking lizard tails in beer, or putting bits of smoked fish in dandelion wine — all came out really awful. *sigh* Guess it's up to me to work it out myself, then.

f70dd3811570b239.voiceContent: Oh, Beidou is the greatest! Every time I go out sailing with her, she always manages to fish up lots of fresh ingredients! Octopus tentacles go great in soup, and seaweed fries up great with some chilis. Not just Beidou, but everyone on board The Crux loves my cooking.

4b2c253bb5ec98da.voiceContent: I've come across a lot of fussy eaters, but Mr. Zhongli is very particular and has no problem getting straight to what he has to say. The first time I served him salt and pepper tofu, he took just one bite, and then proceeded to say It would be better to try sea salt extracted from the shallow seas of Guyun Stone Forest, because it would bring a fresh sense of depth to the tofu. I tried it and the taste was just so different! He's just amazing, don't you think!?

65f00a32a59c7be0.voiceContent: Roasted pigeon skewers, anyone? C'mon, it's my secret recipe, you'll love it!

0f2f7819f0491e47.voiceContent: My master did a good job teaching me spear fighting, don't you think? If you want, I could teach you too. Although... I'd much rather teach you my cooking, if you're interested! I want my recipes to spread all around Teyvat!

b98456236f1b0bbe.voiceContent: My heart's desire? To start my very own cooking tradition, of course! Li-style and Yue-style cooking are good, but they have a limited palate. The missing ingredient? Chili pepper! Come, let me fry up one of Guoba's chili peppers for you...

23d88408e352592d.voiceContent: I think I've won you over with my cooking now, right? It's time to introduce you to my latest masterpiece — I call it the most marvelous multi-colored super pancake! Bright red squirrel ham, orange carrot, yellow sunfrog meat, green calla lily and blue butterfly wings, beautifully wrapped in a thin egg pancake— What? I thought you said you were starving! *sigh* Okay.

b4f46a11c1b5e49c.voiceContent: I'm in a dilemma and I don't know how to solve it... It isn't like me to get so worked up over nothing... Ah! Well, here's the thing. I always love getting you to try my latest recipes, but... I'm worried that my food might not agree with your stomach and... I can't bear the thought of that happening. What should I do?

7e5df3c5fb688a84.voiceContent: Watch carefully! Heat the oil in a pan, then take a handful of crystalflies — wings removed — pop them in, and voila! Delicious deep-fried crystal— Hey! Where are you going?

ef3ded85f43f5119.voiceContent: It's been a month and I still haven't sold a single bowl of Mushroom Slime Stew. Gee, is it just because it looks sticky and gooey? It's their loss if they don't have a spoonful...

2aaa920c80451bff.voiceContent: My favorite thing to eat is... whatever exotic ingredient I haven't tried yet! No, I'm not dodging the question, that's my honest answer!

8b20323a27234d19.voiceContent: I'll eat absolutely anything! There are no bad ingredients, only bad cooking!

26990b109d1c1598.voiceContent: Mmm! I know this taste, it's... boom shaka-laka!

d0fcb8aba3683b92.voiceContent: I gotta admit, you're really good at cooking. Next time, it's my turn to show you a thing or two.

4169201bbedbea3e.voiceContent: Are you sure you followed the recipe? Something is definitely off here...

1ef267813bf7b0b5.voiceContent: Ah, there you are! Come with me, I've prepared a birthday feast all for you! ... No really, I insist! Which dish is your favorite? It's okay, take your time, try them all first, then let me know!

52279b4c4bc7f953.voiceContent: Oh wow! This feels great! My whole body is bursting with energy!

e7d36d66d790abbc.voiceContent: Hey! Ha! Hua! I can slay a beast with one punch, locking in that freshness!

56b7875df92d204d.voiceContent: Finally... with this power, I can cook... *giggle* ...Oh no, I've started salivating!

943ed9760e11a15e.voiceContent: As my father always says To make a five-star dish, you need ten-star passion! I know, I know! To be able to come this far is definitely thanks to your ten-star passion when it comes to practicing with me, so I'll be sure to pay you back with two— no, three times the passion!

d3add2140b550c41.voiceContent: Now I'm really in a pickle!

565ff9aae5429177.voiceContent: Help! My dinner is attacking me!

5c06914c065d91e8.voiceContent: Xinyan always comes to the Wanmin Restaurant for a late-night snack! She gobbles up all the new dishes that the likes of Xingqiu and Chongyun don't go near... and nine times out of ten, she enjoys them too! She's great.

a4a113d5139b8140.voiceContent: Yelan? Of course, I remember her! When I first met her, I was certain she'd be the kind of gal who'd prefer lighter dishes... turned out that she can handle the most spice out of all my customers! Apparently, my dishes weren't spicy enough for her, because she started taking bites of raw Jueyun Chilis! Truly amazing.

7c9ab2506e4b0170.voiceContent: Oh boy, once I know Gaming is coming, I make sure to prepare a huge pot of tea in advance. You know, so he can wash some of the spicy food down. I've offered to tone down the spice a bit for him, but he absolutely insists that he prefers the authentic flavor... And he's not even just saying that to be polite. Believe me, I know a true foodie when I see one! Anyway, if that's what he prefers, then who am I to disappoint, hehe!

3f7b77ef09958b44.voiceContent: Guoba loves Lan Yan! They spent soooooo long shaking hands when they first met, it was like they'd known each other forever, haha. Lan Yan actually promised to take me foraging for wild mushrooms and insects... Hehe, once my new dish is ready, you've gotta come try it!

684d8273b0dde53c.voiceContent: Who taught you how to play? Can they teach me, too?

74f1c707e7185c1b.voiceContent: Wow, there's so many people here to play... You think they'll get hungry?

2c18c41f54464e08.voiceContent: Alright! I'll show you what I'm made of!

eb6192073cac6a4f.voiceContent: Haha, now that's what I call a win!

69a4300f800c3f66.voiceContent: Waaah, I completely messed up there...

05f00bbb9c730bb9.voiceContent: At least it was still a close game...

220fdde355b94698.voiceContent: Heading out? Hmm, I should probably go think about what to cook later...

85ff4b769735d660.voiceContent: One piping-hot victory, fresh from the oven! Hehe!

41642608466ab7ae.voiceContent: I gotta admit, you're really good at cooking. Next time, it's my turn to show you a thing or two.

d86180621083afda.voiceContent: Are you sure you followed the recipe? Something is definitely off here...

36cef31ae0e57934.voiceContent: Mmm! I know this taste, it's... boom shaka-laka!

8a1dea2bace85a22.voiceContent: Uh oh, things are getting spicy!
